name: Horrors of Our Own
description:
Imagination becomes reality within the Tapestry.
Even illusory friends, spawned by the minds of mere children, persist in this land, still desiring the same companionship they once brought to their makers.
However, as time passes and the shadow of oblivion and solitude consumes them, desire turns into bitterness and love turns into hatred.
Thus, the products of our imagination become our worst nightmares.
